title: In the 2023 BUET admission test, all 50 students in the top 50 merit list secured positions, and a total of 1,290+ students qualified out of 1,309 seats.
In the 2023 Medical admission test, all 50 students in the top 50 national merit list, including 241 students at DMC, secured positions. A total of 4,300+ students qualified out of 5,380 seats.
In the 2023 DU ‘Ka’ Unit admission test, all 50 students in the top 50 merit list secured positions, and a total of 1,800+ students qualified out of 1,851 seats.
In the 2023 CKRUET admission test, all 50 students in the top 50 merit list secured positions, and a total of 3,180+ students qualified out of 3,231 seats.
